PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain persons as directors of the board of directors of the St. John's Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Terence Pike, St. John's, Newfoundland, in the place of Arthur Puddister, whose term has expired; David Murphy, Topsail, Newfoundland, in the place of Paul Reynolds, whose term has expired; and Marbeth Andrews, St. John's, Newfoundland, in the place of Michael J. Walsh, whose term has expired)
